SUMMARY:Velvet Fog at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:The Velvet Fog is a Marin County–based rock band known for delivering high-energy\, near-album-quality performances of classic and modern favorites. Drawing from rock\, blues\, alternative\, and even a touch of country\, their setlist spans legendary artists from Queen and David Bowie to Queens of the Stone Age and The Black Keys. With seasoned musicianship and a crowd-pleasing sound\, The Velvet Fog brings a dynamic live show that keeps audiences dancing and singing along. \nFor Social Sunday at the Roadhouse\, expect an eclectic mix of timeless rock anthems and modern hits\, performed with style\, groove\, and plenty of good vibes
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/velvet-fog-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
